AGES: 18+ ONLY  NO REFUNDS | ALL SALES FINAL
VIP Table Packages available email mike@nightculture.com
Text DANCE to 545454 for the latest in Houston Electronic Music News & Info
 
Tickets: After completing your purchase on Eventbrite, you will receive an email confirmation with your attached PDF ticket(s).  You MUST print and bring your PDF tickets AND VALID PHOTO IDENTIFICATION to be admitted for the event.  You may download the Eventbrite app and show your ticket on your mobile device for entry in lieu of printing. Ticket Transfer Policy: You may gain entry to the event even if your name is not on your ticket ONLY so long as the barcode is scannable.  Disco Donnie Presents and NightCulture are not responsible if ticket(s) cannot be scanned and the order is under a different name than the person presenting the ticket.
Please do not post a photo of your ticket publicly in order to avoid the potential risk of a stolen bar code.  Tickets are treated like cash and cannot be replaced if lost or stolen. 
TICKET REMINDER:To ensure your satisfaction, Disco Donnie Presents and NightCulture cannot guarantee tickets purchased from un-authorized 3rd party resellers (individuals or brokers). We recommend that you purchase tickets directly through discodonniepresents.com, eventbrite.com, our authorized partners, and the venue box offices. Questions: tickets@discodonniepresents.com or tickets@nightculture.com
Tickets are limited to 8 per person. Anyone purchasing more than 8 tickets will be automatically refunded for the number of tickets exceeding this limit. 
For more information visit discodonniepresents.com and nightculture.com
bandsintown_response.title: Anjunadeep @ Stereo Live in Houston, TX
